org.glassfish.admin.amx.core

Class AMXValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glassfish.admin.amx.core.AMXValidator

  • @Taxonomy(stability=UNCOMMITTED)
public final class AMXValidator
extends Object
    Validation of key behavioral requirements of AMX MBeans. These tests do not validate any MBean-specific semantics, only general requirements for all AMX MBeans.

    Note that all tests have to account for the possibility that an MBean can be unregistered while the validation is in progressâ€” that is not a test failure, since it is perfectly legal.
